schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: Nestled in the woods, your fully remodeled mountain cabin awaits! Located in The Villas close to the Lake Arrowhead Village, the famous Tudor House, and HWY 18 for convenient access. This home would be great for both full time living or a rental/vacation home. Truly unique in its updated yet rustic charm. Upstairs, you are greeted by the wrap around deck surrounded by trees. Inside you'll love the new kitchen cabinets, new quartz countertops, and new appliances. The full bathroom features a new vanity, sink & fixtures. LVP flooring throughout with living room fireplace adjacent to 2 bedrooms. The lower level features a large bedroom, a full bathroom thats been completely remodeled with a new vanity & sink, new light fixtures, new toilet, new vinyl shower & trim kit, new drywall & paint and a separate indoor laundry room. This home is also easily convertible into a duplex with separate entry downstairs that can provide an additional source of income. Not pictured is the BRAND NEW DRIVEWAY! This location is GREAT for commuting, as it's one of the first roads in The Villas plowed during winter months. Don't miss this!
